410
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:15,200
earnings report for the market they

411
00:19:11,919 --> 00:19:18,320
trade. They still rely on their pivot or

412
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:20,799
Ballinger setups for entry triggers. You

413
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:24,320
